                <note rend="inline" type="source">C.P.(Gen)Doc.1.U.22.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Article 69</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1946-10-15T23:59:59+01:00" notBefore="1946-07-29T00:00:00+01:00">undated</date>
                </dateline>
                <list>
                    <label>1.</label>
                    <item>In the first sentence of paragraph 1, replace the words: “coming into
                        force of the present treaty belong to Italy or to Italian nationals …” by:
                            <quote rend="blockquote">
                            <p>“entry into war against the Allied Power concerned, belonged to Italy
                                or Italian nationals or which were acquired between the entry into
                                war and the coming into force of the present treaty …”</p>
                        </quote>
                    </item>
                </list>
            </div>
